product_name: L'OrealBrow Stylist Definer Waterproof Eyebrow Pencil
summary: SummaryThe L'Or√©al Brow Stylist Definer makes filling in your brows easy. The fine tip draws tiny brow hairs and precisely defines, while the spoolie easily blends.
details: DetailsBenefitsPrecisely defines & draws tiny brow hairsUltra-fine 0.5MM tip recreates tiny brow hairs & fills in sparse areasSoft spoolie brush defines & blends final lookFeaturesWaterproofMechanical & retractable pencil has a spoolie brush for combing and blending the perfect browItem 2575099How To UseStart with clean, brushed brows. Using the Ultra-fine tip pencil, draw the outline of your brow shape. Fill in the gap with light feathered strokes. Comb up following your arch shape using the soft blending brush for a more defined look.Eye cosmetics in a scratched, infected or irritated eye and scratches from cosmetic eye applicators can lead to eye damage, and in extreme cases, even blindness. If your eye is scratched, stop using all eye cosmetics and go to an ophthalmologist immediately. Never apply this product in a moving vehicle.IngredientsDiisostearyl Malate, Triethylhexanoin, C20-40 Acid, C20-40 Alcohols, Synthetic Wax, Polyethylene, Glyceryl Behenate / Eicosadioate, Ethylene / Propylene Copolymer, Ethylcellulose, Boron Nitride, VP / Eicosene Copolymer, Zinc, Tocopherol, Silica, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil / Sunflower Seed Oil, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Tin Oxide. May Contain: CI 77491, CI 77492, CI 77499 / Iron Oxides, Mica, CI 77891 / Titanium Dioxide, CI 77007 / Ultramarines, CI 77163 / Bismuth Oxychloride, CI 77000 / Aluminum Powder, CI 77400 / Bronze Powder, CI 77510 / Ferric Ferrocyanide, CI 75470 / Carmine.
how_to_use: Start with clean, brushed brows. Using the Ultra-fine tip pencil, draw the outline of your brow shape. Fill in the gap with light feathered strokes. Comb up following your arch shape using the soft blending brush for a more defined look.Eye cosmetics in a scratched, infected or irritated eye and scratches from cosmetic eye applicators can lead to eye damage, and in extreme cases, even blindness. If your eye is scratched, stop using all eye cosmetics and go to an ophthalmologist immediately. Never apply this product in a moving vehicle.
ingredients: Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil / Sunflower Seed Oil

reviews.headline: Great Product
reviews.comments: I love this brow pencil. I there are nice, realistic, shades to choose from and the pencil is nice and precise. It wears well. No fading throughout the day. I don't have a con.

reviews.headline: One of the Best Eyebrow Pencils!
reviews.comments: The twist up base is easy to use & the pencil doesn't break when applied to fill in brows. The spoolie on the opposite end combs your brows before or after application. Easily removed with eye makeup remover & the color doesn't fade or travel once applied. It's also a good bargain when comparing more expensive eyebrow pencils.

reviews.headline: LOVE
reviews.comments: Comparable to high end brow pencils. This shade of black is perfect without being too bold. Formula is smooth and long lasting, without breakage or weird waxiness.

reviews.headline: Misleading
reviews.comments: I dont mind this product but is not anywhere near waterproof. Thats what i was looking for so its a no for me

reviews.headline: Comparable to  Lanc√¥me's brow styler at a third of the price
reviews.comments: I recently fell in love with the Lanc√¥me brow pencil. But spending $30 a month is out of the question.  I put two and two together and found the perfect solution by the same company.

reviews.headline: Not My Favorite, but It Gets the Job Done
reviews.comments:
I thought I would give this product a try because I didn't want to spend the money on the ABH this time. I really like having the brow brush and the color that matched my brows (I picked up the Ash Brown shade). The color blended in with my brows and stays on all day.

My problem with this product is that the crayon portion is very fragile. I have had it break before and during application. I feel like there's a lot of wasted product because of this issue.

faceoff_positive.comments: The major change in my life I had to make in this pandemic was to learn how to do my eyebrows. I had no idea but my bangs would no longer cover my brows at work anymore. I bought L'Or√©al because I like a lot of their productsAnd  learned how to apply. When I wore it into the covid unit I thought to my self oh please let my eyebrows last 12 hours and well here is a picture from the start of my shift the the end and I can't be any more happy!!!!
faceoff_positive.headline: My best friend!

faceoff_negative.comments: I buy at least one of these a week, I love the brand and the color fits me perfectly but I'm spending at least $50 a month just on eyebrow pencils! It's ridiculous, I love it I just wish it was cheaper or had more in the package. Not sure if I'll be buying much longer.
faceoff_negative.headline: Quality not enough quantity
